  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 15-20 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Deseed the <strong>red peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>olive oil</strong> </span>over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> with a big pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Cook over a high heat for 3 min until charred around the edges</p>\n<p>Once charred, reduce the heat to low, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for a further 10-15 min until softened and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>black beans</strong></p>\n<p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, half of the <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and mix well </p>\n<p>This is your <strong>chipotle dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the<strong> halloumi</strong> in half, then each half into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> <strong>sticks</strong></p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\n<p>Trim then finely slice the<strong> spring onion</strong><strong>s</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the peppers are caramelised, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, the remaining <strong>red wine</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> and drained <strong>black beans</strong> and cook for a further 2 min until the beans have warmed through</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>peppers</strong> and <strong>beans</strong> to the drained <strong>brown rice</strong> (reserve the pan for the next step!) – this is your <strong>Mexican rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wipe down the pan and return it to a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi sticks</strong></p>\n<p>Cook on each side for 2 min until golden</p>\n<p>Tip: alternatively cook on the BBQ until golden and slightly charred!</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/469_-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>spring onion</strong> to the <strong>Mexican rice</strong> and mix well</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>halloumi sticks</strong> over the <strong>Mexican rice</strong> with the <strong>smoky dressing</strong> drizzled over</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
